  "original_title": "\u0dc1\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0dd3 \u0dbd\u0d82\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dc0\u0dad\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db4\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dd2 \u0da2\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Another great win for Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Sri Lankan team managed to record a 4-wicket victory in the match between the Sri Lankan team and the Afghanistan team, starting the Super Four round of the Asian Cup.",
        "The Afghanistan team, who batted first in the match, managed to score 175/6 in the allotted 20 overs.",
        "The Sri Lankan team played the reply innings and won the match by collecting 179 runs for 6 wickets in 19.1 overs.",
        "Bhanuka Rajapaksa scored 31 quick runs in 14 balls for Sri Lanka and brought the match to Sri Lanka."
      ],
